Package hu.bme.mit.theta.core.dsl.gen

Interface CoreDslListener

All Superinterfaces:
org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeListener
All Known Implementing Classes:
CoreDslBaseListener
public interface CoreDslListener extends org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeListener
This interface defines a complete listener for a parse tree produced by CoreDslParser.
